    excerpt_en: `Brazil's central bank regularly updates its rules for international money transfers. Staying compliant protects your funds and ensures smooth transactions. Here's what changed and what remains constant.`,
    excerpt_zh: `巴西中央银行定期更新其国际汇款规则。保持合规可以保护您的资金并确保交易顺畅。以下是发生变化的内容和保持不变的内容。`,
